creator: Andreas Flosdorf
descriptionHtml:
SIMPLE AND EASY TO USE FEATURES

- Load GPX (route & track) and KML files in a clear and modern design without advertising.

- View loaded routes and start a simulation to inform yourself about the environment, plan your tour and preload maps.

- Start the navigation - Routes guides you along the loaded route and informs you immediately when the route has left. A recording is running at the same time.

- Navigation in the background and with headphones or alternatively with display always on.

- The Speech Assistant supports you in handling this app and during a navigation.

- Recorder function to find the right way without a preloaded route and to save the completed track for later.

- Enter a coordinate (latitude/longitude) to navigate to a specific location.

- Many small features and settings which match your individual needs of appearance and behavior.


Whether hiking, biking, skiing or other outdoor activities ... with Routes you will never lose the right path! Routes allows you to load your own planned or otherwise provided routes from your favorite portals such as Goolge, AllTrails (Gpsies), Polar, Garmin (and many others). Routes supports the file formats GPX and KML. After opening a file in Routes, you can start a simulation or start navigating directly. In any case, Routes guides you along the track. If you ever lose the track, Routes will notify you visually and by alarm. It is not necessary to always keep an eye on the display. You can concentrate fully on your route and enjoy the beautiful things on it.

More Information on: http://route-navigation.flosdorf.net

Have fun with Routes!


- We like your feedback (mail@routes-navigation.de) rather than a bad rating much better! :)
If you like Routes, then we look forward to your positive rating.

Routes is powered by: Android, Google Play Services, Google Firebase, GitLab, Deepl Translator (https://www.deepl.com/), Renderforest (https://www.renderforest.com/de/), Freepik (https://de.freepik.com/), Wordpress (Theme: SoSimple by http://www.fernandovillamorjr.com/)
descriptionShort: GPX / KML Navigation, Simulation & Recorder - Let Routes guide you reliable!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
The most frequently requested functions are currently being created and tested. In the meantime, we want your Routes to run 100% smoothly.
You may not be able to *see* the changes, but we have made some corrections and improvements.
Feel free to send us your questions and suggestions to 'mail@routes-navigation.de'.
Have fun with Routes!

- Start a simulation to get a preview about the environment, plan your tour and preload online maps.

- Start the navigation - Routes guides you along the loaded route and informs you immediately when the route has left. A recording is running at the same time.

- Navigation can run in background, with headphones or alternatively with display always on.

- The Speech Assistant supports you in handling this app and during a navigation.

- Recorder function to find the right way without a preloaded route and to save the completed track for later.

- Enter a coordinate (latitude/longitude) to navigate to a specific location.

- Many useful features like altitude profile, auto gpx interpretation, individual display settings, landscape and portrait mode, picture in picture navigation, geocaching, dark mode and much more…

Whether hiking, biking, skiing or other outdoor activities ... with Routes you will never lose the right path! Routes allows you to load your own planned or otherwise provided routes from your favorite portals such as Goolge, AllTrails (Gpsies), Polar, Garmin (and many others). title: Routes - GPX KML Navigation & GPS Tracker

creator: Andreas Flosdorf
descriptionHtml:
SIMPLE AND EASY TO USE FEATURES

- Load GPX (route, track & geocache) and KML files in a clear and modern design without advertising.

- On selected offline and online maps you can explore the environment.

- Start a simulation to get a preview about the environment, plan your tour and preload online maps.

- Start the navigation - Routes guides you along the loaded route and informs you immediately when the route has left. A recording is running at the same time.

- Navigation can run in background, with headphones or alternatively with display always on.

- The Voice Assistant supports you in handling this app and during a navigation.

- Recorder function to find the right way without a preloaded route and to save the completed track for later.

- Enter a coordinate (latitude/longitude) to navigate to a specific location.

- Many useful features like altitude profile, auto gpx interpretation, individual display settings, landscape and portrait mode, picture in picture navigation, geocaching, dark mode and much more…

Whether hiking, biking, skiing or other outdoor activities ... with Routes you will never lose the right path! Routes allows you to load your own planned or otherwise provided routes from your favorite portals such as Goolge, AllTrails (Gpsies), Polar, Garmin (and many others). Routes supports the file formats GPX and KML. After opening a file in Routes, you can start a simulation or start navigating directly. In any case, Routes guides you along the track. If you ever lose the track, Routes will notify you visually and by alarm. It is not necessary to always keep an eye on the display. You can concentrate fully on your route and enjoy the beautiful things on it.

For more Information please visit: http://routes-navigation.de

title: Routes - GPX KML Navigation & GPS Tracker

creator: Andreas Flosdorf
descriptionHtml:
SIMPLE AND EASY TO USE FEATURES

- Load GPX (route, track & geocache) and KML files in a clear and modern design without advertising.

- On selected offline and online maps you can explore the environment.

- Start a simulation to get a preview about the environment, plan your tour and preload online maps.

- Start the navigation - Routes guides you along the loaded route and informs you immediately when the route has left. A recording is running at the same time.

- Navigation can run in background, with headphones or alternatively with display always on.

- The Voice Assistant supports you in handling this app and during a navigation.

- Recorder function to find the right way without a preloaded route and to save the completed track for later.

- Enter a coordinate (latitude/longitude) to navigate to a specific location.

- Many useful features like altitude profile, auto gpx interpretation, individual display settings, landscape and portrait mode, picture in picture navigation, geocaching, dark mode and much more…

Whether hiking, biking, skiing or other outdoor activities ... with Routes you will never lose the right path! Routes allows you to load your own planned or otherwise provided routes from your favorite portals such as Goolge, AllTrails (Gpsies), Polar, Garmin (and many others). Routes supports the file formats GPX and KML. After opening a file in Routes, you can start a simulation or start navigating directly. In any case, Routes guides you along the track. If you ever lose the track, Routes will notify you visually and by alarm. It is not necessary to always keep an eye on the display. You can concentrate fully on your route and enjoy the beautiful things on it.

For more Information please visit: http://routes-navigation.de

title: Routes

creator: Andreas Flosdorf
descriptionHtml:
SIMPLE AND EASY TO USE FEATURES

- Load GPX (route, track & geocache) and KML files in a clear and modern design without advertising.

- On selected offline and online maps you can explore the environment.

- Start a simulation to get a preview about the environment, plan your tour and preload online maps.

- Start the navigation - Routes guides you along the loaded route and informs you immediately when the route has left. A recording is running at the same time.

- Navigation can run in background, with headphones or alternatively with display always on.

- The Voice Assistant supports you in handling this app and during a navigation.

- Recorder function to find the right way without a preloaded route and to save the completed track for later.

- Enter a coordinate (latitude/longitude) to navigate to a specific location.

- Many useful features like altitude profile, auto gpx interpretation, individual display settings, landscape and portrait mode, picture in picture navigation, geocaching, dark mode and much more…

Whether hiking, biking, skiing or other outdoor activities ... with Routes you will never lose the right path! Routes allows you to load your own planned or otherwise provided routes from your favorite portals such as Goolge, AllTrails (Gpsies), Polar, Garmin (and many others). Routes supports the file formats GPX and KML. After opening a file in Routes, you can start a simulation or start navigating directly. In any case, Routes guides you along the track. If you ever lose the track, Routes will notify you visually and by alarm. It is not necessary to always keep an eye on the display. You can concentrate fully on your route and enjoy the beautiful things on it.

For more Information please visit: http://routes-navigation.de

title: Routes

creator: Andreas Flosdorf
descriptionHtml:
SIMPLE AND EASY TO USE FEATURES

- Load GPX (route, track & geocache) and KML files in a clear and modern design without advertising.

- On selected offline and online maps you can explore the environment.

- Start a simulation to get a preview about the environment, plan your tour and preload online maps.

- Start the navigation - Routes guides you along the loaded route and informs you immediately when the route has left. A recording is running at the same time.

- Navigation can run in background, with headphones or alternatively with display always on.

- The Voice Assistant supports you in handling this app and during a navigation.

- Recorder function to find the right way without a preloaded route and to save the completed track for later.

- Enter a coordinate (latitude/longitude) to navigate to a specific location.

- Many useful features like altitude profile, auto gpx interpretation, individual display settings, landscape and portrait mode, picture in picture navigation, geocaching, dark mode and much more…

Whether hiking, biking, skiing or other outdoor activities ... with Routes you will never lose the right path! Routes allows you to load your own planned or otherwise provided routes from your favorite portals such as Goolge, AllTrails (Gpsies), Polar, Garmin (and many others). Routes supports the file formats GPX and KML. After opening a file in Routes, you can start a simulation or start navigating directly. In any case, Routes guides you along the track. If you ever lose the track, Routes will notify you visually and by alarm. It is not necessary to always keep an eye on the display. You can concentrate fully on your route and enjoy the beautiful things on it.

For more Information please visit: http://routes-navigation.de

Have fun with Routes!


- We like your feedback (mail@routes-navigation.de) rather than a bad rating much better! :)
If you like Routes, then we look forward to your positive rating.

descriptionShort: GPX KML navigation, simulation & gps tracking - Let Routes guide you reliable!

You are also welcome to send us your questions and suggestions to mail@routes-navigation.de
Have fun with Routes!

- Recorder function to find the right way without a preloaded route and to save the completed track for later.

- Enter a coordinate (latitude/longitude) to navigate to a specific location.

- Many useful features like altitude profile, auto gpx interpretation, individual display settings, landscape and portrait mode, picture in picture navigation, geocaching, dark mode and much more…

Whether hiking, biking, skiing or other outdoor activities ... with Routes you will never lose the right path! Routes allows you to load your own planned or otherwise provided routes from your favorite portals such as Goolge, AllTrails (Gpsies), Polar, Garmin (and many others). Routes supports the file formats GPX and KML. After opening a file in Routes, you can start a simulation or start navigating directly. In any case, Routes guides you along the track. If you ever lose the track, Routes will notify you visually and by alarm. It is not necessary to always keep an eye on the display. You can concentrate fully on your route and enjoy the beautiful things on it.

For more Information please visit: http://routes-navigation.de

Have fun with Routes!


- We like your feedback (mail@routes-navigation.de) rather than a bad rating much better! :)
If you like Routes, then we look forward to your positive rating.
